Programming is a way to give instructions to the computer , may be sequential instructions ,
selections or looping instructions 

we have to give exact steps

Program will be those exact steps written in a programming language

what is Ecmascript ?
ECMAScript is the standards / specifications on which Javascript is based.

JavaScript and ECMAScript can almost be always used interchangeably


